{"title":"数列特征","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"url":"http://www.tsinsen.com/A1008","statement":[{"title":"","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div id=\"pcont1\" style=\"margin-top:20px; display:block;\">\n"},{"title":"# 问题描述","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　给出n个数，找出这n个数的最大值，最小值，和。</div>"},{"title":"# 输入格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　第一行为整数n，表示数的个数。(1&lt;=n&lt;=10000)<br/>\n　　第二行有n个数，为给定的n个数，每个数的绝对值都小于10000。</div>"},{"title":"# 输出格式","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pdcont\">　　输出三行，每行一个整数。第一行表示这些数中的最大值，第二行表示这些数中的最小值，第三行表示这些数的和。</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输入","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">5<br/>\n100 40 -30 30 1</div>"},{"title":"# 样例输出","format":"html","require":["katex"],"content":"\n<div class=\"pddata\">100<br/>\n-30<br/>\n141</div>\n\n</div>\n"}]}